c2_native_run_net will do the computation @anderspapitto.

The only concern is if we have some random generator, we may slightly change the semantic. That's a fundamental problem... the caffe2's init_net does not totally equal to the onnx's initializers.

body:
`c2_native_run_net` will do the computation @anderspapitto.

The only concern is if we have some random generator, we may slightly change the semantic. That's a fundamental problem... the caffe2's init_net does not totally equal to the onnx's initializers.
